channel.title: Please PM me all IP's to working servers with newest items!
channel.description:
If you own a server, or know the IP to one that has new items I.E. Skill capes, Dragon Full Helm, Changed Rares (Black PHAT, White Halloween mask, ect.) Please PM me, I would greatly appreciate it. Also if you own one, and need a Co-Owner, I am a good Java Coder, and I own several servers of my own. I am willing to help anyone in need. Thanks for reading, remember to PM me IP's!
|Runer King|
